Steven,

Hi, in my experience, popping thru the carbs at idle indicates a lean at
idle condition.  Are you able to adjust the mixture adjust screws to
accommodate your situation?  Perhaps 1 size larger idle jets are in order?  

Check this out, it will help you.

http://www.aircooled.net/gnrlsite/resource/articles/dualcarb.htm

Good luck!

